[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":136},["ShallowReactive",2],{"post":3,"content-query-0lN3MsYOfd":87},{"_path":4,"_dir":5,"_draft":6,"_partial":6,"_locale":7,"title":8,"description":9,"imagesource":10,"imagecredit":10,"image":11,"createdAt":12,"updatedAt":12,"readingTime":13,"body":16,"_type":81,"_id":82,"_source":83,"_file":84,"_stem":85,"_extension":86},"/posts/stop-slackware-renaming-network-devices","posts",false,"","Stop Slackware from Renaming Network Devices","How to modify Slackware's udev rules to ensure consistency in network device naming.",null,"2011.11.11T150000_stop-slackware-renaming-network-devices.jpg","2011-11-11T15:00:00",{"text":14,"minutes":15,"time":15,"words":15},"0 min read",0,{"type":17,"children":18,"toc":78},"root",[19,27,32,37,57,68,73],{"type":20,"tag":21,"props":22,"children":23},"element","p",{},[24],{"type":25,"value":26},"text","Hi guys!",{"type":20,"tag":21,"props":28,"children":29},{},[30],{"type":25,"value":31},"Yet another short post this time!",{"type":20,"tag":21,"props":33,"children":34},{},[35],{"type":25,"value":36},"I've been building machines, which have to be totally interchangeable, and discovered that when I swapped a hard drive between motherboards, that Slackware would increment the ethernet device(s). eth0 would become eth1, eth0 and eth1 would become eth2 and eth3. What's worse, if I plugged a few different wireless dongles in, every single one would have a new number! This was an utter pain in the backside for trying to use code which assumed eth0 or wlan0; also, it seemed ridiculous that we could end up with systems with completely different configurations, so I set out to find how to stop this happening.",{"type":20,"tag":21,"props":38,"children":39},{},[40,42,48,50,55],{"type":25,"value":41},"The offending configuration file was ",{"type":20,"tag":43,"props":44,"children":45},"em",{},[46],{"type":25,"value":47},"/lib/udev/rules.d/75-persistent-net-generator.rules",{"type":25,"value":49},". This causes udev to keep track of the MAC addresses of the network interface, and to assign a persistent interface name. It creates the file ",{"type":20,"tag":43,"props":51,"children":52},{},[53],{"type":25,"value":54},"/etc/udev/rules.d/70-persistent-net.rules",{"type":25,"value":56}," and populates it with a rule for every new device attached.",{"type":20,"tag":21,"props":58,"children":59},{},[60,62,66],{"type":25,"value":61},"To stop this evil behaviour, simply delete the generator file (",{"type":20,"tag":43,"props":63,"children":64},{},[65],{"type":25,"value":47},{"type":25,"value":67},").",{"type":20,"tag":21,"props":69,"children":70},{},[71],{"type":25,"value":72},"Nice and simple!",{"type":20,"tag":21,"props":74,"children":75},{},[76],{"type":25,"value":77},"n00b",{"title":7,"searchDepth":79,"depth":79,"links":80},2,[],"markdown","content:posts:2011-11-11-stop-slackware-renaming-network-devices.md","content","posts/2011-11-11-stop-slackware-renaming-network-devices.md","posts/2011-11-11-stop-slackware-renaming-network-devices","md",{"_path":4,"_dir":5,"_draft":6,"_partial":6,"_locale":7,"title":8,"description":9,"imagesource":10,"imagecredit":10,"image":11,"createdAt":12,"updatedAt":12,"readingTime":88,"body":89,"_type":81,"_id":82,"_source":83,"_file":84,"_stem":85,"_extension":86},{"text":14,"minutes":15,"time":15,"words":15},{"type":17,"children":90,"toc":134},[91,95,99,103,117,126,130],{"type":20,"tag":21,"props":92,"children":93},{},[94],{"type":25,"value":26},{"type":20,"tag":21,"props":96,"children":97},{},[98],{"type":25,"value":31},{"type":20,"tag":21,"props":100,"children":101},{},[102],{"type":25,"value":36},{"type":20,"tag":21,"props":104,"children":105},{},[106,107,111,112,116],{"type":25,"value":41},{"type":20,"tag":43,"props":108,"children":109},{},[110],{"type":25,"value":47},{"type":25,"value":49},{"type":20,"tag":43,"props":113,"children":114},{},[115],{"type":25,"value":54},{"type":25,"value":56},{"type":20,"tag":21,"props":118,"children":119},{},[120,121,125],{"type":25,"value":61},{"type":20,"tag":43,"props":122,"children":123},{},[124],{"type":25,"value":47},{"type":25,"value":67},{"type":20,"tag":21,"props":127,"children":128},{},[129],{"type":25,"value":72},{"type":20,"tag":21,"props":131,"children":132},{},[133],{"type":25,"value":77},{"title":7,"searchDepth":79,"depth":79,"links":135},[],1734162516047]